## General notification and email settings

### Notifications

In**WP admin  Voxel  Settings  Notifications** you can select:

- Admin user: This user will receive all notifications that are set to Notify admin
- Select how long to keep in-app notifications in the database (days). By default, this is set to 30 days

### Emails

In**WP admin  Voxel  Settings  Emails,** you can configure some of the data associated with email notifications, including:

- Sender name
- Sender email
- Email footer text
